{"tid":1595822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實FC對我地既國際戰線好重要","createTime":"2019-09-26T08:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T11:11:02.000Z","uid":61757,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"60e6ddcecae4ca1ae383cbd9dc3bbf3edb9f37a8","tid":1595822,"uid":61757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:48:56.000Z","msg":"係tg gp見到，講FC，好認同，有時間睇睇同幫推<br />\n<br />\n有位本地記者同Admin們接觸，俾左D有關於呢場運動既意見我地，可以避免重複雨傘既失敗，又可以增加呢場運動係國際上既關注：<br />\n<br />\n1. 關於FC<br />\n<br />\nA. FC從來唔係receive and forward，對每一條報既料，特別係事關重大既一定要打爛沙盤問到篤。<br />\n<br />\nB. 未證實既野廣傳，會影響到其他手足或現場情況，更甚者影響外媒對我地呢場運動既信任。<br />\n<br />\n2. FC對外媒既重要性<br />\n<br />\nA. 外媒係會follow TG GP同埋Channel，順手可以搵受訪目標；<br />\n<br />\nB. 外媒對全球既影響力比本地新聞機構大，所以如果佢地接觸既資訊係假，會令佢地覺得我地想誣捏政府，令自己得到更加多勝算，影響外國人對運動既關注；<br />\n<br />\nC. 外國人唔再關注，某程度上係自我滅聲嘅行為。<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動黎到呢到，大家都好努力，無人想因為小事而摧毀左呢百幾日既努力。大家都唔知道呢場運動完左，我地會唔會有下一次。可以做既就無各盡本身做好自己，Admin們亦會盡本份做好FC既工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/fcairport/1726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffcairport%2F1726&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=9fe7b3be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fcairport/1726</a>"},{"pid":"ea345be646d55984701c845fc022ee4e3e885fde","tid":1595822,"uid":61757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:51:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4721a02f8f5db34fbfc49e19eb5dcbdba3098125","tid":1595822,"uid":51641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:58:57.000Z","msg":"咁如果對家不斷扮我地forward未FC既野呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ea49fa48f5b71ff10a35d2ba96582ff98576fe","tid":1595822,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:03:07.000Z","msg":"記者天職唔係求真咩<br />\n<br />\n點解講講下好似要平民查好晒再比料佢地登咁？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔同意d鳩up野都亂傳，例如前兩日張死人名單"},{"pid":"20ca6a2e51fb5a31aea8ed512fde1b67a91c17d1","tid":1595822,"uid":278180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:04:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a11ec4dea8445cc9e31b395ae07a2d0448efe254","tid":1595822,"uid":61757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:18:40.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"d61d883e0a564fbb6c02be8e8812175ac6b88ba5","tid":1595822,"uid":61757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4721a02f8f5db34fbfc49e19eb5dcbdba3098125","tid":1595822,"uid":51641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:58:57.000Z","msg":"咁如果對家不斷扮我地forward未FC既野呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:19:15.000Z","msg":"所以我地更加要做好fc"},{"pid":"d4df9c75ff9ede518510d75ac9a61b22f7bb14c0","tid":1595822,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:21:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a22305ef25196e8957c1d3543406212786a49f11","tid":1595822,"uid":79602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:23:27.000Z","msg":"外國人要查 好難 因語言不通<br />\n又要快<br />\n仲要日日都有大量野報<br />\n<br />\n所以先會出現要FC清楚比記者報"},{"pid":"40c4a9f506bceae605a05c9b3c15a12301dca3fb","tid":1595822,"uid":61757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9f8c222f538449b8246d9824048acee33bb1174f","tid":1595822,"uid":61757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:42:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d5a9f976ec796d90040bb95b4985aa32cd134356","tid":1595822,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:51:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af7da0fe908a5de10c4b15306d2b4e6a74322984","tid":1595822,"uid":233009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:52:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b2a732eed9538ab0d2c49b0a3718d7a1fd85b1e9","tid":1595822,"uid":61757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:14:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"197d5adc03df7a4e8adab67dbb81b86cff1b0186","tid